attributionInfo.brokerName: EAGLE REAL ESTATE AND PROPERTY MANAGEMENT INC.
EAGLE REAL ESTATE AND PROPERTY MANAGEMENT INC.

data.description: Here’s a Beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath Home with a great semi open floor plan. As you enter you will be pleasantly surprise with its nicely sized living room and its well located cozy fireplace for those cool winter nights, this living space over looks a spacious Dining area with its lovely custom built in display cabinetry, this dining area is nicely situated between both living room and its gorgeous kitchen for a great semi open floor plan. You’ll love showing off this beautiful kitchen with its lovely matching cabinets perfectly topped off with beautiful Granite counter tops which also perfectly decorates the backsplash from the counter tops to the upper cabinets, its a beautiful sight! From here You’ll have access to the garage, but wait, there’s an empty space between the kitchen & the garage just waiting for a new idea, maybe a mud room, a pantry, or? Now onto the 2 car garage which includes storage cabinets and a laundry area, no interrupting washer and dryer noise in this lovely Home. As you return to the dining and living room You will have access through a sliding glass door to a very nicely sized covered concrete patio over looking some fruit trees, oranges and avocados to name a few. As for the bedrooms, 2 are nicely sized with carpet flooring and spacious closets these rooms both share a well sized hall bathroom which has a bath tub shower combo. Down the hall is the larger of the 3 bed rooms with it’s own private bath room including its own shower stall. This is a beautiful home closely situated off the 215 & the 60 freeways and a short distance to the UCR campus, and not too far from, yet not too close to the well known down town Riverside. Yes the pictures are nice to have, but I believe you can tell that this is a Must see Home, could this possibly be Your next Home? Don’t hesitate!!
